  "text": "As far as the scaling symmetry of Φ (X 7 in [CITATION_1] ) is concerned, we do not agree with Frewer and Khujadze. This symmetry is present also in other methods used to describe stochastic fields, namely the multipoint correlation function approach and the multipoint probability density function approach; see [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , where also its physical meaning was discussed.",
